{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21631.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":101601,"motion":200,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":101701,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"*Clatter* *Rumble*...","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21631.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":101701,"lipSynch":0}],"nameRight":"Mitama","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"id":101601,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Kanagi","textLeft":"..."},{"bgm":"bgm03_story06","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":101701,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"Hey, why did you tag along with me today?"},{"chara":[{"id":101701,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"Do you realize where we're going? The Neo-Magius@is waiting for us, you know?"},{"chara":[{"id":101601,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Kanagi","textLeft":"Yes, I'm fully aware...@Are you surprised?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":101701,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"I wouldn't say I'm \"surprised\"...@Well, maybe a little..."},{"chara":[{"id":101701,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"Once we've heard the Neo-Magius out, I'm not sure@we'll be able to decline."},{"chara":[{"id":101701}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"Also, aren't you more fond of everyone@in Kamihama than I am?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"id":101601,"lipSynch":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kanagi","textLeft":"..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.4,"bg":"bg_adv_16151.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":100}],"nameCenter":"Kanagi","textCenter":"Apologies, but I like Tamaki and Nanami@more than I realized.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.4,"bg":"bg_adv_21631.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":101701,"motion":1,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":101601,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":101701}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"In the East alone, you've still got Ryo's@feelings to carry with you.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":101701}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"You have so many loved ones,@both at home and at work..."},{"chara":[{"id":101701,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"I didn't think you could bring yourself to wish for@Kamihama's demise anymore."},{"chara":[{"id":101601,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Kanagi","textLeft":"I'm not quite as detached from it all as you are."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101601}],"nameLeft":"Kanagi","textLeft":"And suppose I did accomplish my goal,@I would still be ridden with guilt."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"id":101601,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kanagi","textLeft":"As I watch the future generation—our successors—@be consumed by the darkness plaguing the@East and West,"},{"chara":[{"id":101601}],"nameLeft":"Kanagi","textLeft":"I can't help but feel resigned towards this town@that's stagnated throughout history..."},{"chara":[{"id":101701,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"Was...someone throwing a rock at Mii@what started this...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"id":101601,"lipSynch":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kanagi","textLeft":"..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.4,"bg":"bg_adv_13162.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":103801,"motion":400,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":801300,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":801400,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"chara":[{"id":801300}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Just like this!","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"[flashEffect:flashWhite2]*Whoosh*","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_060.exp3.json","id":103801}],"nameLeft":"Mikage","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"[flashEffect:flashRed2][chara:103801:effect_shake]Agh!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":101701,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":101601,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.4,"bg":"bg_adv_21631.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":101601,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":101701,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":101601}],"nameLeft":"Kanagi","textLeft":"...It's not that simple.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":101601,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Kanagi","textLeft":"I wouldn't make a blanket judgement@over a single incident."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101601}],"nameLeft":"Kanagi","textLeft":"...Now it's not just Mikage getting hurt,@but others as well."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":101701,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"You sound awfully angry..."},{"chara":[{"id":101701}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"Did something happen to your family...?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101601,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Kanagi","textLeft":"...Things are only going to get worse from here."},{"chara":[{"id":101601},{"id":101701,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Kanagi","textLeft":"Our future may have become unbearable@to look at..."},{"chara":[{"id":101601,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kanagi","textLeft":"Then at the very least,"},{"chara":[{"id":101601}],"nameLeft":"Kanagi","textLeft":"I must be willing to burn the past to the ground@to save the future."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":101601,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Kanagi","textLeft":"My biggest concern is whether or not@the Neo-Magius will be powerful enough..."},{"chara":[{"id":101601}],"nameLeft":"Kanagi","textLeft":"...to bring about destruction, given that they've@lost their top brass..."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_21221.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":101601,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":101701,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"*Jangle* *Jangle*","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"nameCenter":"Miyuri's Voice","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"Ah, o-over— over heeere~!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":101601},{"effect":"fadeout","id":101701}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21221.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":103101,"motion":1,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":103201,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":103101},{"effect":"fadeout","id":103201}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102301,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":102501},{"effect":"fadeout","id":102301}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":101601,"lipSynch":0,"motion":400,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp3.json","id":101701,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Kanagi","textLeft":"...!"},{"chara":[{"id":101701}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"That's the Tokime's...!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
